				<p><b>With Other Users and Third Parties.</b> Other Users can only see the personal information that a User enters into his or her Website profile, which generally will include the User's name, email address, and city and state of residence, plus any additional information that a User voluntarily decides to include in the profile. Blendedd will not share a User's mailing address, phone number, or credit card information with other Users without the express consent of the User. Except as set forth above or as otherwise authorized by you, Blendedd will not disclose, sell, trade, or otherwise transfer personal information to any third party. Blendedd shall in no event be liable to you for any use or misuse of personal information by any third party with whom your personal information has been shared in accordance with the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>
