				<p>Even after account modification or removal, copies of previous information may remain on the Website to the extent that it had been previously shared with other Users. In addition, Blendedd may retain certain information in order to prevent identity theft and other illegal activities after an approved deletion. Removed information may remain in archives, but will not be available to other Users or third parties.</p>
