				<h3>How do we Protect User Information ?</h3>
				<br />
				<p><b>Information Security.</b> Blendedd will use a variety of security precautions to protect the security and integrity of all User information, in accordance with this Privacy Policy and all applicable laws. Each User's personal information is protected in several ways. Access by a User to his or her personal information is available through a password and unique customer ID selected by the User. This information is encrypted through the Website with Secure Socket Layer technology (SSL) and is also encrypted when it is stored by Blendedd to prevent unauthorized parties from viewing such information. Also, Blendedd performs regular malware scanning of the Blendedd website and all servers and computers used by Blendedd to support the Website. All Blendedd employees are required to adhere to Blendedd's security and confidentiality procedures and undergo training related to maintaining the security of User personal information.  </p>
				<p>In order to most efficiently serve our Users, credit card transactions are handled by established third-party banking and processing agents. They receive the information needed to verify and authorize your credit card or other payment information.</p>
